title: River City Books' Deli
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Small deli inside book store sells a small selection of organic produce and products, and offers vegan take-out options such as in-house-made sesame tofu, soups, and deli salads. Is located in the same small building as Fine Thyme Cafe, but is a different business with a different menu.
